I FIXED IT

I think Windows 7 was blocking Chatchitto from pasting into program folder, so i manually dumped the crack to the desktop and manually copied it.

-When you launch installer, Choose last choice on bottom "Virtual DJ v7.0 PRO CRACK".

-Extract crack anywhere like your desktop.

-Manually copy the crack "virtualdj_pro.exe" to your program folder. Default is C:\Program files/VirtualDJ

Program works now :)
